keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.

map n scrollDown
map e scrollUp
map N previousTab
map E nextTab
map i scrollRight
map t LinkHints.activateMode
map T LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map f createTab
map F Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map I goForward

unmap j
unmap J
unmap k
unmap K
unmap l
unmap L
